OL,3,CWelsh police join forces for M4
OL,4,Cuninsured drivers crackdown
OL,6,FTwo forces have taken part in a major
OL,7,Foperation to crack down on uninsured
OL,8,Fvehicles.
OL,10,FOfficers from and joined the Avon &
OL,11,FSomerset, Wiltshire and Thames Valley
OL,12,Fforces in tracking suspected uninsured
OL,13,Fvehicles across the M4.
OL,15,FWelsh force seizures for uninsured
OL,16,Fvehicles in 2023 totalled 5,228 -
OL,17,Faveraging 14 vehicles being seized
OL,18,Fevery day.
