OL,6,F"Using the software we have available
OL,7,Fto us, the units out on patrol are
OL,8,Fable to identify those vehicles and
OL,9,Fthen intercept them along the bringing
OL,10,Fthem to the check site", explained Sgt
OL,11,FSean Fletcher, from Gwent Police.
OL,13,F"The power that we have to seize
OL,14,Fvehicles is not there as a punishment
OL,15,Fin itself, it's there to prevent that
OL,16,Fvehicle continuing a journey or
OL,17,Fanother journey.
