OL,6,FIf the situation allows, and the
OL,7,Fdriver can insure the vehicle then and
OL,8,Fthere, then of course discretion is
OL,9,Fallowed, but sometimes it's safer for
OL,10,Fus and the public that we remove the
OL,11,Fvehicle from the road altogether."
OL,13,FThe MIB - Motor Insurers Bureau - has
OL,14,Fhelped coordinate the joint operation.
OL,16,FIt told ITV Wales the day resulted in
OL,17,Fan additional 51 vehicle seizures,
OL,18,Fplus 5 arrests and 7 prosecutions for
OL,19,Fother offences.
