OL,6,F"Whilst we work with the police
OL,7,Fthroughout the year, supporting forces
OL,8,Fin designating time to focus on
OL,9,Funinsured driving allows this issue to
OL,10,Fbe tackled head on in a targeted way"
OL,11,Fsays Martin Saunders, Head of
OL,12,FEnforcement at MIB.
OL,14,F"We know the benefits will be widely
OL,15,Ffelt across all different areas of the
OL,16,Fforce and the community, making the M4
OL,17,Fand surrounding areas safer."
